+- `lib/hive/paths.rb` (`Hive::Paths`) — XDG resolver with legacy back-compat + asset resolver.
+- `lib/hive/install_channel.rb` (`Hive::InstallChannel`) — brew/aur/bash/unknown detection.
+- `lib/hive/service.rb` (`Hive::Service`) — launchd/systemd service registration + uninstall.
+- `lib/hive/commands/update.rb`, `lib/hive/commands/uninstall.rb`.
+- `lib/hive/commands/init/prompts.rb` (`GlobalPrompts`) — first-run global config collection.
