+
+1. Tebako + bubbletea/lipgloss FFI native libs — feasibility spike (Risk #1) not yet run; `packaging/tebako/build.sh` gates on it. FUQ #1 (vendored Ruby vs. brew `depends_on "ruby"`) unresolved.
+2. `.hive/` vs `.hive-state/` rename — kept `.hive-state/` for v1 (FUQ #2); rename deferred unless the user confirms.
+3. `jq` — dropped from the dep check (FUQ #3); not in `packaging/deps.txt` or `Doctor::DEPS`.
+4. `hive`/`hv` fallback scope — bash one-liner only; brew/AUR install canonical `hive` (FUQ #4).
+5. Agent marketplace command names — unconfirmed (FUQ #5); install prompt prints manual instructions and stops when a marketplace-add command can't be determined.
